{"tid":323940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「 床上國共合作」 郭文貴驚爆：1998年國民黨高官與藉和談與中國女星上床","createTime":"2017-07-16T05:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:13.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889397080fb7c6f6c5c33a60dde1130d3976c7af","tid":323940,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"「床上國共合作」 郭文貴驚爆：1998年國民黨高官與藉和談與中國女星上床<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-16 12:47<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕流亡美國的中國富豪郭文貴，屢次爆出中國高層內幕，例如他透露中共中紀委書記王岐山和范冰冰、許晴曾有性交易，還指出王岐山外甥姚慶所負責的海航集團，有幾個男人在飛機上把女星弄到休克。郭文貴昨日則自稱丟出「核彈級」爆料，<span style=\"color: red;\">那就是1998年台灣國民黨高官，曾和中國女星在床上談「國共合作」。</span><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴15日的直播爆料影片長達1小時18分，他在影片尾端談到，他如果要踢爆台灣的事情，那麼很多人都會破產，而且不敢再待在台灣。郭文貴說，1998年的時候，中共總政聯絡部在北京四環買了3棟別墅，聯絡台灣國民黨人士、重要企業家等人前來，完成一次次的「國共合作」。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴說，<span style=\"color: red;\">有1個錄像非常驚人，可以看到1個國民黨的高官，以及當時國家（中國）最火的女明星，那位明星為了國家利益就跟高官睡覺，兩人還在床上親密地說「這是真正的國共合作」。</span><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴指出，在那些別墅發生太多事情了，商人、國民黨人士、軍方人士，1個個都被拿下來了，所以現在如果他要爆台灣的料，他相信許多人一定都很緊張。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2133495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2133495&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=166bf06e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2133495&h=3838577e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2133495</a>"},{"pid":"48919c4acb88029b4b73a1eef19c417eb6c39089","tid":323940,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b419e3480e837fd5a94b96fa5d7c54584ffdfbf","tid":323940,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9c6447a98da4358267c830e1386532890db0c4","tid":323940,"uid":73623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:06:21.000Z","msg":"肯出片未<br />\n得個講字"},{"pid":"de3ac6299f40195f3f4012f1d98d8abca1789317","tid":323940,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"條友永遠純文字"},{"pid":"56da2e403ffd2b85a22d213a83473083773fa391","tid":323940,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"Youtuber 又出片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec89789237f686c2730316cfea9ee45463abefb","tid":323940,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"條友吹水唔抹嘴"},{"pid":"11b2d3b3dcbea7e289157edaeb064072703fc544","tid":323940,"uid":91789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"不孝既極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89f59dd095e1575108d7d6a79dacda8a71a0d88","tid":323940,"uid":42295,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"你話系就系?"},{"pid":"599e4e41b51fd72ef23f3f4f2c00c01af61c7e7f","tid":323940,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2f14775fa47ccc2333117e8130f1007518ab884","tid":323940,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"佢根本拿唔出任何證據"},{"pid":"02dd4abc01a46e85e6a47e70e6e823f45ca06471","tid":323940,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"190670c0d6a7b67633c35b77e349270b2b2a5c39","tid":323940,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話系就系?</blockquote><br />\n系你老母"},{"pid":"c7228210cdf19b7f4cada45d0b3a5310cdf666f6","tid":323940,"uid":61280,"li